      "content": "it's just that \"finding someone to sit with you\" sounds like more effort. more talking, more explaining, more pretending to be okay while i'm just waiting for the next thing to collapse. i don't want to \"heal\" or \"integrate\" anything anymore. i just want the weight to be gone. i've spent my whole life fighting to stay upright, and i'm just so done with the struggle. i just want to find some kind of peace that isn't dependent on me having to keep trying every single day.",
